      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Many people are familiar with the idea that their odds of getting struck by lightning are one in a million, when the odds are more precisely around 1 in 500K.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "That said, the odds of dying from a lightning strike in your lifetime is somewhere around 1 in 15,000. Which means you have better odds of dying from smoking, skydiving, or scuba-diving.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Here’s the thing. Does this mean you are unlikely to die from a lightning strike?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Of course it does.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "But does it mean that it",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "won’t",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "happen to you?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Certainly not.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "When you hear about",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "people",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "who died from something as rare as being struck by lightning, its often because of two things:",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-0",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-57801398"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "listItem": "number",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "They didn’t think it would happen to them—because of overconfidence and the deception of statistics.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "listItem": "number",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "They did something that increased their odds of it happening—almost certainly because they didn’t think it would happen to them.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Point is, stats are deceiving. Low odds plus arrogance is a deadly combination.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}